Ranger Help for: locate
=======================

SYNTAX:      locate
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     15
SKILL TYPE:  husbandry

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to sense the location of their bonded animal
follower. The Ranger receives information about which direction and
approximately how far away their companion is. This skill only works in
wilderness terrain. If the follower has died, the skill will report that
no companion can be found. Locate is useful when the Ranger and their
follower have become separated.
